This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with learning sentence representations. The use of Recurrent Neural Networks (RNNs) and linear models also suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also mentions the use of self-supervision, which is a common theme in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) research. Additionally, the paper discusses the use of multi-view learning, which could be relevant to cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) sub-categories.
